 here: [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4:"Amit";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5004:"<p>Today we are happy to announce that we have 2 themes and 2 plugins to add to our compatibility list. The themes are <a title="Neighborhood" href="http://themeforest.net/item/neighborhood-responsive-multipurpose-shop-theme/5086341">Neighborhood</a>, <a title="Quins" href="http://themeforest.net/item/quins-bs-creative-wordpress-themes/7037698">Quins</a>, and the plugins are <a title="WP Ultimate Recipe" href="http://www.wpultimaterecipe.com/">WP Ultimate Recipe</a> and <a title="Slash Admin" href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/slash-admin/">Slash Admin</a><br />\nIf you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a title="Multilingual Ready Themes " href="https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a title="Multilingual Ready Plugins " href="https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you&#8217;re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a title="Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins" href="https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center">Neighborhood theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/neighborhood-responsive-multipurpose-shop-theme/5086341"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493" src="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/neighborhood.png" alt="ekho" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Neighborhood is super responsive, retina ready, and built upon the 1170px Twitter Bootstrap framework. Featuring a clean, modern, and superbly slick design, packed with the most powerful Swift Framework which offers limitless possibilities.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/neighborhood-responsive-multipurpose-shop-theme/5086341" target="_blank">Download Neighborhood theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center">Quins theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/quins-bs-creative-wordpress-themes/7037698"><img src="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/quins.png" alt="ekho" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Creative WordPress portfolio/agency Theme with clean and modern design.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/quins-bs-creative-wordpress-themes/7037698">Purchase Quins theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center">WP Ultimate Recipe plugin</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.wpultimaterecipe.com/"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493" src="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/recipe.png" alt="ekho" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>A beautiful and user-friendly recipe plugin for WordPress.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.wpultimaterecipe.com/">Download WP Ultimate Recipe plugin</a>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center">Slash Admin plugin</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/slash-admin/"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493" src="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/slash.png" alt="ekho" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Slash Admin gathers some common functions and lets you change various different options in a WordPress website.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/slash-admin/">Download Slash Admin plugin</a>\n</div>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=MkB_g0dzGeQ:mGg6yJBzmg0:D7DqB2pKExk"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=MkB_g0dzGeQ:mGg6yJBzmg0:D7DqB2pKExk" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=MkB_g0dzGeQ:mGg6yJBzmg0:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=MkB_g0dzGeQ:mGg6yJBzmg0:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=MkB_g0dzGeQ:mGg6yJBzmg0:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=MkB_g0dzGeQ:mGg6yJBzmg0:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/MkB_g0dzGeQ" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:101:"https://wpml.org/2015/03/this-week-compatible-neighborhood-quins-wp-ultimate-recipe-slash-admin/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explic