(350, 1, '2014-07-16 21:03:18', '2014-07-16 21:03:18', '<p>Like every year, Europlus Direct got to enjoy another fantastic day of Team Building activities on June 24<sup>th</sup>. While last year’s event took us climbing and orienteering on the Keighley Moors, this year took everything up a notch.</p>\r\n<p><img class=" size-full wp-image-352 aligncenter" src="http://europlusdirect.localhost/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Pic-1-Team-Building.png" alt="Pic-1-Team-Building" width="481" height="338" /></p>\r\n<p>In the morning we all met up at Checkered Flag Go Karting in Guiseley. (<a href="http://www.chequeredflag-karting.com/" target="_blank">http://www.chequeredflag-karting.com/</a>) We were divided into 4 teams, given safety instructions, overalls and helmets and off we went into an endurance race that gave Le Mans a run for its money! Between 3 of us we had to drive 200 laps with a minimum of 50 laps each which sounds a lot easier than it is!</p>\r\n<p>A few crashes and no champagne shower later, we went on to the Cow and Calf in Ilkley. The Harrogate Climbing Centre (<a href="http://www.harrogateclimbingcentre.com/" target="_blank">http://www.harrogateclimbingcentre.com/</a>) kindly gave us a crash course in abseiling and then put this straight into action by making us walk backwards down a sheer cliff. While this may have been the scariest thing quite a few of us have ever done, everyone had a good go at it, overcoming their fears.</p>\r\n<p><img class=" size-full wp-image-351 aligncenter" src="http://europlusdirect.localhost/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Pic-2-Team-building.png" alt="Pic-2-Team-building" width="482" height="327" /></p>\r\n<p>To calm our nerves (though not our pulse) we then went on to another orienteering walk over the Ilkley Moors, all the way down to White Wells. Each team was sent to 3 different points on the moors where small packages were hidden which contained parts of a puzzle. With all three packages collected, everyone made it back to the Cow and Calf Pub around 4pm to put their puzzles together and go through which team had collected the most points for their activities throughout the day.</p>\r\n<p>Everyone really enjoyed the whole day, not only because it’s nice to do something outside of the office every once in a while but because the different activities gave everyone a chance to try themselves at something they wouldn’t normally do.</p>\r\n<p>A huge thanks to the organisers, surely we’ll have another great day next year!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Europlus Direct – Team Building Day 2014', 'Like every year, Europlus Direct got to enjoy another fantastic day of Team Building activities on June 24th. While last year’s event took us climbing and orienteering on the Keighley Moors, this year took everything up a notch.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'europlus-direct-team-building-day-2014', '', '', '2015-04-21 22:52:06', '2015-04-21 22:52:06', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_news&#038;p=350', 0, 'cpt_news', '', 0),
